text.tspan: "En kraftig maltet ale,
med 4 malt-typer, bla
skotsk tørverøget malt.."
- albryg.dk
Wee Heavy
Scottish
Ale
U
V
Keldling Bryg
This is a Brewolution all grain beer, supposed to reach 7,7%
alchohol, EBC 32 og IBU 35. The mashing wasn't too effective
so it is more likely to be 6,7% alchohol. A rather plumb wort -
named "mosevand" (bog water) by my wife - turned into a rather
fine amber coloured beer. Should possible be stored 3 - 6 months
after end of carbonation Saturday 13th of February 2016.
"It looks bad, havin' to rush oout again straight awa'" - "Aye. Tis comp-li-cat-ed." -
"Including, I am sorrrry to say, an aerial attack by the otherwise quite attractive fey ..."
- "A kelda would see the clear way hersel." - "Ach, noo yer talkin oour language."
- "I'm biggerrr on the inside!" - "The Wee Free Men" by Terry Pratchett
